import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data['day'] = pd.to_datetime(data['day'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data['day_of_week'] = pd.Categorical(data['day_of_week'], categories=['Monday','Tuesday','Wednesday','Thursday','Friday','Saturday', 'Sunday'], ordered=True)
    data = data.sort_values('time')
    daily_count = data.groupby('day')['count'].mean()
    daily_count.plot(kind='line', figsize=(10,6), color='blue')
    plt.axhline(y=daily_count.mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Average Count')
    plt.title('What is the average count of events per day?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):

    data = data.sort_values('day_of_week')
    chart = data.groupby('day_of_week')['count'].sum().plot(kind='bar', color='blue')

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['hour'] = pd.to_datetime(data['hour'], format='%H:%M:%S', errors='coerce').dt.hour
    hour_count = data.groupby('hour')['count'].sum()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.bar(hour_count.index, hour_count.values, color='blue')
    ax.set_xlabel('Hour of the Day')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of events by hour of the day?')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['time'] = pd.to_datetime(data['time'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data['hour'] = data['time'].dt.hour
    data = data.groupby(['hour', 'time']).mean().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    for key, grp in data.groupby(['hour']):
        ax = grp.plot(ax=ax, kind='line', x='time', y='count', label=key)
    plt.title('What is the average count of events per hour?', wrap=True)
    plt.axhline(y=data['count'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Average Count')
    plt.legend(loc='best')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
